#: ../../../userspace-api/media/mediactl/media-ioc-device-info.rst:34
msgid ""
"All media devices must support the ``MEDIA_IOC_DEVICE_INFO`` ioctl. To query "
"device information, applications call the ioctl with a pointer to a struct :"
"c:type:`media_device_info`. The driver fills the structure and returns the "
"information to the application. The ioctl never fails."
msgstr ""

