#: ../../../userspace-api/media/mediactl/media-ioc-device-info.rst:94
msgid ""
"The ``serial`` and ``bus_info`` fields can be used to distinguish between "
"multiple instances of otherwise identical hardware. The serial number takes "
"precedence when provided and can be assumed to be unique. If the serial "
"number is an empty string, the ``bus_info`` field can be used instead. The "
"``bus_info`` field is guaranteed to be unique, but can vary across reboots "
"or device unplug/replug."
msgstr ""

